regiment Nina Kulangina

00:01:36.550 --> 00:01:39.700 align:middle line:10%
made international headlines
by demonstrating a series

00:01:39.700 --> 00:01:42.160 align:middle line:10%
of astounding psychic powers.

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:45.190 align:middle line:10%
Mainly focusing on her
psychokinetic abilities,

00:01:45.190 --> 00:01:48.730 align:middle line:10%
Russian scientists studied
Kulangina in a series of tests

00:01:48.730 --> 00:01:52.030 align:middle line:10%
ranging from moving objects
and influencing laser beam

00:01:52.030 --> 00:01:56.170 align:middle line:10%
trajectories to the stopping
of a frog's beating heart,

00:01:56.170 --> 00:01:59.650 align:middle line:10%
all using only her mind.

00:01:59.650 --> 00:02:02.500 align:middle line:84%
Nina could even generate
electromagnetic heat

00:02:02.500 --> 00:02:03.730 align:middle line:90%
with her body.

00:02:03.730 --> 00:02:05.710 align:middle line:84%
