passion to pursue,

00:02:49.870 --> 00:02:53.772 align:middle line:84%
how do I develop my ability
so that I can help others?

00:02:53.772 --> 00:02:56.910 align:middle line:10%
>> If psychic abilities
are indeed a reality,

00:02:56.910 --> 00:03:00.000 align:middle line:10%
it stands to reason that world
governments would realize

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:03.120 align:middle line:10%
the huge potential in
utilizing such skills,

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:07.830 align:middle line:10%
particularly in the fields
of defense and intelligence.

00:03:07.830 --> 00:03:12.510 align:middle line:10%
In 1975, the CIA tasked two
laser physicists, Dr. Russell

00:03:12.510 --> 00:03:16.650 align:middle line:10%
Targ and Hal Puthoff, to develop
a psychic spy program that

00:03:16.650 --> 00:03:20.070 align:middle line:10%
spent more than $20
million over 20 years

00:03:20.070 --> 00:03:23.910 align:middle line:10%
testing, developing, and
applying psychic abilities.

00:03:23.910 --> 00:03:28.410 align:middle line:84%
>> So I formed, together with
my colleague Hal Puthoff,

00:03:28.410 --> 00:03:33.030 align:middle line:84%
