program at Stanford Research

00:03:33.030 --> 00:03:34.190 align:middle line:90%
Institute.

00:03:34.190 --> 00:03:37.800 align:middle line:84%
But we felt that
during the Cold War,

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:40.710 align:middle line:84%
