demonstration-of-ability task

00:03:54.270 --> 00:03:57.660 align:middle line:84%
to do and that was
successful, and we then

00:03:57.660 --> 00:04:01.340 align:middle line:90%
had a 20-year research activity.

00:04:01.340 --> 00:04:05.220 align:middle line:84%
>> The fact that the CIA spent
millions in taxpayer dollars

00:04:05.220 --> 00:04:08.850 align:middle line:84%
over decades investigating
psychic abilities does lend

00:04:08.850 --> 00:04:11.400 align:middle line:84%
credence to the
phenomenon's legitimacy.

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:13.740 align:middle line:84%
