them repeatedly.

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:32.085 align:middle line:10%
This individual's
name was Uri Geller.

00:04:32.085 --> 00:04:33.960 align:middle line:10%
>> They were very concerned.

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:39.270 align:middle line:10%
The CIA were concerned that
the Russians were ahead

00:04:39.270 --> 00:04:41.610 align:middle line:10%
