and Russel Targ and Edgar

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:57.210 align:middle line:10%
Mitchell, and all
those scientists who

00:04:57.210 --> 00:05:00.030 align:middle line:10%
had very direct
links to the CIA,

00:05:00.030 --> 00:05:03.210 align:middle line:10%
they set up their
experiments with me.

00:05:03.210 --> 00:05:06.330 align:middle line:84%
>> Investigations into Uri
Geller's powers covered

00:05:06.330 --> 00:05:09.690 align:middle line:84%
the gamut of psychical areas,
though his ability to use

00:05:09.690 --> 00:05:13.620 align:middle line:84%
