bend a spoon was what he is most

00:05:13.620 --> 00:05:15.770 align:middle line:90%
famous for.

00:05:15.770 --> 00:05:20.800 align:middle line:84%
>> I hold a spoon and I
stroke it very gently,

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:28.380 align:middle line:84%
